title: Danvers Youth Football Yearbook: Christian Bleicher
text: Posted Oct. 21, 2015 at 4:41 PM Updated at 4:41 PM Posted Oct. 21, 2015 at 4:41 PM DANVERS How many years playing DYF: 6 Positions: Linebacker, Split End, Cornerback, Safety, Halfback, Defensive Tackle Other sports you play: None Favorite subject in school: Math Favorite TV show: Family Guy What type of music do you like? Rap Do you have a favorite band? Big Sean, and Drake Most memorable moment in DYF: One-handed interception to end the game against North Reading Who is your role model, and why? My Aunt Cristina, who graduated from BU summa cum laude with a double major. Wicked Local
